headline: CMS Energy (CMS) Misses Q1 Earnings Estimates
summary: CMS Energy (CMS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.86% and 9.04%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
